    title: "How to Get a GEA Event Permit in Saudi Arabia: Complete 2026 Guide",
    excerpt: "Step-by-step guide to obtaining a GEA entertainment permit in KSA — requirements, processing times, costs, and the most common mistakes event planners make.",
