      "So, how do you actually make your [corporate event](/services/corporate-events) or [conference](/services/conferences) eco-friendly without cutting corners on quality? Let us break it down.",
      "## 1. Choose a Green Venue",
      "When picking a venue, ask these important questions:",
      "- Does the venue have **LEED certification** or any environmental certifications?",
      "- Do they have **recycling bins** and proper waste management?",
      "- What is their policy on **single-use plastics**?",
      "- Do they use **energy-efficient lighting and water-saving systems**?",
      "More and more international companies are making this a deal-breaker, so choosing the right venue matters a lot.",
      "## 2. Reduce Waste (It Is Easier Than You Think!)",
      "Here are simple, practical changes that make a big impact:",
      "- **Go digital:** Use digital invitations and event apps instead of printed brochures and paper programs.",
      "- **Ditch the plastic:** Use reusable or compostable plates, cups, and cutlery for catering.",
      "- **Recycle on-site:** Set up clearly labeled recycling stations around the venue.",
